    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Dann Corbit</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:173px;\"><a href=\"http://www.quarkchess.de/belct/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b6/Dann_corbit.jpg\" width=\"171\" height=\"211\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Dann_corbit.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dann Corbit <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Dann Corbit</b>,<br />\nan American software developer, computer chess expert, programmer, tester and advisor. He is author of the chess program <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bean_Counter&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bean Counter (page does not exist)\">Bean Counter</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, and along with <a href=\"/Colin_Frayn\" title=\"Colin Frayn\">Colin Frayn</a>, co-author of the chess program <a href=\"/Beowulf\" title=\"Beowulf\">Beowulf</a>  <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \nDann has further compiled various <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">test suites</a>, notably <a href=\"/Silent_but_Deadly\" title=\"Silent but Deadly\">Silent but Deadly</a>, and along with <a href=\"/Swaminathan_Natarajan\" title=\"Swaminathan Natarajan\">Swaminathan Natarajan</a> co-authored the <a href=\"/Strategic_Test_Suite\" title=\"Strategic Test Suite\">Strategic Test Suite</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe was involved in an international project called <a href=\"/index.php?title=C.A.P.&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"C.A.P. (page does not exist)\">C.A.P.</a> (chess analysis project) and is supporter of a lot of authors of computer chess engines, and active poster in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">computer chess forums</a>. In July 2011, Dann has criticized the <a href=\"/Rybka_Controversy#RybkaDecision\" title=\"Rybka Controversy\">ICGA decision</a> concerning <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a>, stating the design of the investigation process was flawed <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dann_Corbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dann_Corbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=28362\">Speaking of \"Evaluate\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Danniel Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 29, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=44442\">All this talk of cooking is making me hungry. Let's bake a program</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 24, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=45105\">C.A.P. Project completion announcement!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 04, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=70925\">Re: Insomniac</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 28, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bean_Counter&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bean Counter (page does not exist)\">Bean Counter</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=77015\">Re: Dann's multiple cpu program</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 09, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dann_Corbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=405552\">Re: chess engines writen in C</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 13, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30413\">My two cents on the whole ippolit thing</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 31, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Ippolit\" title=\"Ippolit\">Ippolit</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dann_Corbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39531\">Rybka ban thoughts</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 29, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39545\">Voir Dire</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2011 <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65937\">AlphaZero is not like other chess programs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dann_Corbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75358\">Dangerous turn</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 10, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a>, <a href=\"/TCEC\" title=\"TCEC\">TCEC</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dann_Corbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/strategictestsuite/\">Strategic Test Suite</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dann Corbit</a> and <a href=\"/Swaminathan_Natarajan\" title=\"Swaminathan Natarajan\">Swaminathan Natarajan</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dann_Corbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Dann Corbit, Photo from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.quarkchess.de/belct/\">BELCT 2001 Berlin is worth a trip!</a> by <a href=\"/Thomas_Mayer\" title=\"Thomas Mayer\">Thomas Mayer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20081121101914/http://cap.connx.com/C.A.P.%20Biographies/DannCorbit.htm\">C.A.P. Biographies - Dann Corbit</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/strategictestsuite/authors\">Authors - Strategic Test Suite</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.frayn.net/beowulf/index.html\">Beowulf Computer Chess Engine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/strategictestsuite/\">Strategic Test Suite</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120117081610/http://www.top-5000.nl/Rybka.htm\">Rybka vs ICGA a different view</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voir_dire\">Voir dire from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228120945\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 129/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 274/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5272-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228120945 and revision id 21727\n -->\n"
